{
  "stem": "471.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I know-- I know, as a matter of fact, I found the-- the-- hmm, the tomb-- the tombstone, you call it?",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It's not meant-- on the--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "On the cemetery.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You see?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because this was already old cemetery in Cracow, in the heart of city.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Well, they were not-- just before the war, they would not bury there, anymore people.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, my mother comes from-- down-- Tarnow.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My grandparents, from Cracow.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My father's side, Cracow, yes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My mother, not.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My mother comes from Tarnow, which is about 90 kilometers.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And her name was Hertz.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Estera Hertz, yeah.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[BACKGROUND NOISE] I don't know what was going on there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I remember my uncle, which was my mother's brother, every year he used to come for a week and stay with us.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But this was a Jew with a beard like this.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That ?] [? was ?] [? terrible. ?] Everybody had to lay tefillin, every morning.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But believe you me, the day-- the hour he left, the tefillin were put in away till next year, just to make my mother happy, to satisfy my mother.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We did everything for my mother, every-- everybody, everybody.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Give her troubles too, but everybody.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My father had a brother and a sister.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Also, they had lot of children, there, yeah.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yeah, yes.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, the children only survive the war.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But say my aunt didn't.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My uncle didn't.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But they have children.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The children survive.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Only one is living here, and married too, [?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Lola ?] [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And her brother-- oh no, she had two sisters here, I'm sorry, two.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "One is--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The funny thing, I have to-- I have to make a-- a version before.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were talking about the war.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had radio.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We hear the provocation.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
